= | subdivision_type2 = County | subdivision_type1 = State | blank1_info = }} Bonadelle Ranchos-Madera Ranchos was a census-designated place (CDP) in Madera County, California. In 2010, 8,569 people lived there. It has now been split into two CDPs, Bonadelle Ranchos and Madera Ranchos. ==References== Category:Census-designated places in California Category:Settlements in Madera County, California
